# Dr. Sadaqat Ali on Tv Shows

A Nice Subject To Learn

Watch Dr. Sadaqat Ali’s engaging appearances on leading TV shows, where he shares expert insights on [drug addiction Treatment](https://willingways.org/about-us/our-branches/willingways-lahore/), [relationships](https://willingways.org/marriage-counseling-islamabad/), and mental health. Featured on channels like ATV, 92 NEWS, A Plus, and Dunya News, his discussions offer guidance and strategies for personal growth and overcoming challenges.

